{
  "stem": "9963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in fact, that father, he told me-- I have four sons here, but I hope you don't mind that I will adopt you as my fifth son.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, he-- and he did-- and he meant it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He didn't say, because, you know, the things what I did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He meant that with all his heart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I got to know what is happening in every city, so I always made a meeting with him and with this sons, and some other people what they were also, felt responsible.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told them what's happening with that city was evacuated, and that so many people was killed and that city, that city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And our city will be evacuated in that and that day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they asked me how do know this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as much as I loved them, and I respected them, but we knew that kind of situation, you have such a secret where your life depend on it, you cannot share it with nobody even with your own brother.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because sometimes a slip of the tongue can kill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told them, don't ask me that question, because you should know if my life is important to you, so don't ask how I know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So his father right away said, not to even have in mind to ask me anymore anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever I say to take it for good words.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were sitting for hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We hadn't slept the whole night, what we can do in order that everybody should go home to see our parents for the last time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we know what's happening-- what they-- they're taking all the older people, all the sick people, they're killing them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All of the young people, they're putting them in the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We couldn't find a solution.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
